==English==

===Alternative spellings===
* [[meta-puzzle]]

===Etymology===
[[meta-]] (in the transcending, transforming and self-referential senses) + [[puzzle]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A metapuzzle is a puzzle that combines other puzzles to create a compound puzzle.  In contrast to a regular puzzle, a metapuzzle is missing data that is essential to solving it, and which can only be obtained by solving other sometimes entirely unrelated puzzles. Metapuzzles are frequently used in [[puzzlehunt|puzzlehunts]].

